longBusinessSummary: Qatar General Insurance & Reinsurance Company Q.P.S.C., together with its subsidiaries, provides general insurance and reinsurance products. The company offers personal insurance products, such as travel, medical, housemaid, motor, personal accident, jewelry, home, marine hull insurance. It also provides corporate insurance products comprising energy, casualty, property, and other. In addition, the company is involved in the investment, development, and management of real estate properties; repair of automobiles; water bottling and beverage trading; hospitality, exhibition, and events management; and contracting and construction activities, as well as manufacture of rebars and insulation materials. Qatar General Insurance & Reinsurance Company Q.P.S.C. was founded in 1979 and is based in Doha, Qatar.
